Sleeping Beuty

Maleficent cursed the child named Aroura. 
The three faries delayed the curse so that on her 16th birthday she will fell in a sleep like death 
and only true love's kiss will be able to break the curse
Prince philip he fell in love with the princess.
On her 16th birthday Aroura fell in a deep slumber.
Prince Philip went to give the princess true loves kiss but Maleficent turned into a dragon.
Philip defetead Maleficent and saved princess Aroura.
And they lived happily ever after.
The End.
